						<h1>Why people choose us?</h1>
						<p>
							Beach Resort is a mixture of serenity and commercialism, splashed with simple beauty where one can happily lose oneself.  It provides the ideal balance between a pleasant and peaceful stay and the opportunity to explore the sights and sounds of around that area. Beach Resort is a haven of comfort and luxury for a relaxed and quiet stay with friends and family.The resort is surrounded by lush, green gardens and situated bang on the golden sweeping sands of beach. The resort also boasts a multi cuisine beach side restaurant, serving up a good choice of international and local options that is open throughout the day for breakfast, lunch , dinner and snacks and of course for cocktails and drinks.
						</p>
                        <hr />
						<h1>About Us</h1>
						<p>
							The Beach Resort is designed with tranquillity and charm of the beautiful arch shaped beach. The Resort is beautiful in itself.  The hotel is right beside the beach and as the waves lash the parapets of the open-air restaurant, the drone of the restless Arabian Sea lulls to sleep even the most insomniac. The hotel is surrounded by a pair of palm fringed headlands, and the view from each and every room is one that gives you an entire picture of what it is all about.	
						</p>
						<p>
							The Beach Resort serves as one of the best family holiday destinations or for quick getaways. Bask in the sun, dive into the pool, stroll through the garden, cuddle in your bed, feast at our restaurants and allow time to stand still, as you rejuvenate your mind and body.
						</p>
